#### Requirements

1. An online store with PrestaShop infrastructure. This plugin is tested with PrestaShop version 1.4, 1.5, and 1.6.
2. PHP minimum version 5.4.
3. Midtrans plugin for PrestaShop \[ [Github](https://github.com/veritrans/vtweb-prestashop) \| [Zip](https://github.com/veritrans/vtweb-prestashop/archive/master.zip) \].

#### Installation Process

1. Extract the plugin you have previously downloaded and rename folder as **veritranspay**. Then Zip the folder back into veritranspay.zip.
2. Access your PrestaShop *administrator* page.
3. Go to menu **Modules-modules**.
4. Choose *Add a new module*. Upload plugin file **veritranspay.zip**.
5. Find the previously uploaded Midtrans module and click **install**.

#### Plugin Configuration

In order to configure Midtrans-PrestaShop plug-in:

1. Access your PrestaShop admin page.
2. Go to **Modules-modules** menu in PrestaShop admin page.
3. In Veritrans module, click **configure** to enter plugin page.
4. Insert required fields following the figure below.

    ![Prestashop config](/images/presta00.png){: .img-responsive .img-thumbnail}

5. Login to MAP portal to configure a few options below:

    | URL Role | Redirect URL|
    |---|---|
    | Payment Notification URL | http://[your_shopâ€™s_homepage]/index.php?fc=module&module=veritranspay&controller=notification |
    | Finish Redirect URL | http://[your-site-url]/index.php?fc=module&module=veritranspay&controller=success |
    | Error Redirect URL | http://[your-site-url]/index.php?fc=module&module=veritranspay&controller=failure |
    | Unfinish Redirect URL | http://[your-site-url]/index.php?fc=module&module=veritranspay&controller=back |

